Dialogs.Dialog: (Oh no, I'm late！ The girls' practice match was definitely today...)
Oh, it's ▲高嶺＊＊▲'s match！
Hey, how's the match going？
部員Ａ
Isn't it obvious？ Takane will win for sure.
For sure？
She is the best in the girls' tennis club, you know？ On top of that, her looks and grades are top of the class.
She's also the daughter of a doctor...
Wow, is that so...？ She's definitely popular.
Rather than popular... It's more like we live in separate worlds. I mean, you know？
What do you mean？
Takane's a bit stiff. Like, the way she talks. She gives off an aura of "Don't get close to me！"
...Is that so？
Manager
Game set！ Count 3-0. Match won by Takane！
Good work！
Manaka
▲主人公＊▲.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, you were amazing！ It was a complete victory, huh？
Um... Thank you. But, it was just by chance.
No way that was by chance！ You were amazing！
Um... I'll be going.
Okay, sorry...
(You wouldn't think she's the winner from the look on her face...)
(Club activities are over. Guess I'll go home.)
Member
Hey, you're coming too, right？ To Winning Burger.
Winning Burger？ Is there something going on？
We go there sometimes after practice. The girls are joining us too！
All right, let's go. Ah, it's ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Manaka
Then excuse me...
Huh？ ▲高嶺＊＊▲, is she going home？
Oh, she's okay. Let her be...
Why？ We're all getting together, right？ Hey, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
▲主人公＊▲, what is it？
We're all going to Winning Burger. ▲高嶺＊＊▲, won't you join us？
...I think I'll pass. Have fun with everyone.
See？ We live in different worlds. Let's go！
(...Is that right？)
(Practice is over！ Well, I'll head home... Ah！)
Yo, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
Manaka
▲主人公＊▲.
Heading home？ Let's go together.
Um, together？
Yeah... No good？
(Seems like a waste of the moment...)
Can I ask you a question？
...Eh？ Ah, yes.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, why do you always head straight home after practice？
It's fine if you don't want to answer that.
...Is it strange to go straight home after club activities are over？
Well, it's not strange... I guess.
According to school rules, we're supposed to return home immediately after leaving school, right？
School rules？ Hmm... But, you don't need to follow every single one！
Eh？
Well, I'll take my leave here.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, if you are okay, how about we walk home together again？
Ah, but, I can't stop anywhere...
We'll just go straight home. That way, you won't be violating the school rules, right？
If... that's the case... Um, goodbye.
See you later！
(▲高嶺＊＊▲ didn't say no, did she？)
(With all of these people around, it's hard to call out to her...)
(She went in and out of that store three times already... What is ▲高嶺＊＊▲ doing？)
(Rather, what am I doing？ ...All right！)
Yo！ ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
Manaka
▲主人公＊▲.
Well...
It's not. That's not it！
What's not it？
Eh？ I mean, you see... Well...
Let's stop by Winning Burger. I'll treat you for helping me before.
But, stopping on the way home...
Then how about we'll eat quickly and then hurry home？
Well, hehe... Yeah. In that case, I guess it's okay.
Clerk
Welcome to Winning Burger！ What would you like to order？
Manaka
Yes！
Aren't you going to order？
Order？ Ah, yeah. Um, I'd like a hamburger, please.
Do you just want one Winning Burger by itself？
Umm... Yes...
How about Winning Nuggets and a medium Winning Shake with it？ We're having the scratch-ticket double lucky challenge today.
Um, I... Sorry, could you repeat that from the beginning？
(Has ▲高嶺＊＊▲ not been to a fast food restaurant before？)
Okay！ We'll have 2 value meals, and... What would you like to drink？
Drink？ Er, tea...
Then iced tea and a cola...
I'll repeat your order. Two value meals and for drinks...
▲高嶺＊＊▲... You don't come to these places often, do you？
That's not the case. I come every once in a while.
Hmm... Then have you eaten the Mega Teriyaki Noodle Burger？
Mega...？
Last month's special burger.
Of course...
Oh！ I missed out on it. Was it good？ What did it taste like？
Well it was... not sweet or bitter, but very... mega...
I don't really understand
...Did you really try it？
So anyway, was it good？
Well... it's like noodles with teriyaki, but it's not really like that...
Sounds a bit weird...
Well, the taste was complicated...
...Why？
Well, it looks like you're just pretending to know...
I ate it.
Yes, it was very delicious.
▲高嶺＊＊▲ you have such unusual tastes.
Everyone who I talked to said it tasted unpleasant.
(Am I being a bit mean to her？)
It was delicious. Hehe！
Well, isn't that great？
But, it had too much fat and salt. It would be better with half a potato and some milk. Um, adding tomatoes would make it more balanced.
(She was thinking about that while she ate...？)
Then see you later...
Yeah... Um, maybe next time...
Never mind. Thanks for today. Goodbye.
Tezuka
Okay, everybody in！
It's that time you have all been waiting for. The tennis club's annual social mixed doubles！
(Our club is like a casual college club. No wonder we're weak...)
So those who decided on a pair, please write it on the bulletin board. All right, you're dismissed for today！
男女部員
Good work！
Doubles, huh？ What should I do...
Manaka
▲高嶺＊＊▲, you already have a partner, right？ You're the best, after all.
Eh！？ Even though you're the ace？ What about pairing up with your previous partner？
Last time, the girls' had one extra, so I couldn't play... I'm always the last one remaining.
I guess the boys all keep their distance... Well then, is it okay if you pair up with me？
Don't force yourself... I'm used to it, so I'll be fine.
I'm hardly forcing myself...
It's okay. It's the same in class. I'm always the one left out. So really, it's okay.
Then I'll take my leave here.
Okay, see you later...
Um...
Hm？
Never mind. See you later. Goodbye.
Manager
Okay, everybody in！
Today is the deadline for signing up for the mixed doubles tournament. Has anyone not signed up yet？
Yes！ I haven't signed up yet！
What are you going to do？ Are you going to sign up？
Yes, I will enter with Takane-san.
Takane-san, are you okay with that？
Manaka
Um, I... Yes...
All right, then you're dismissed for today！
男女部員
...Good work！
Wait for me. Let's head home together.
Sorry for deciding on my own.
But, you want to play in the mixed doubles matches, right？
Of course, you wanted to play. You're really good and you've been playing since you were little. And besides...
At lunchtime, you clean the clubroom and the courts by yourself... You really like the tennis club, right ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
(Did I upset her？)
You know, if you really don't want to, I can go and cancel our pairing.
That's not it... I'm... happy.
Thanks... I'm really looking forward to it...
Yeah, that's good to hear. Then see you later...
Yeah... see you later.
(Huh？ That's ▲高嶺＊＊▲...)
Manaka
▲主人公＊▲.
What's up, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？ Stopping on the way home？
That's not it！ I just had something I needed to buy at the bookstore...
I was just joking, calm down... So, what did you buy？
A magazine called "Towano Watcher."
I see. A leisure magazine, right？ Are you going somewhere？
Sometimes I tutor the next door grade-schooler. As a reward for getting her grades up, I thought I'd take her somewhere.
Is that so...？ So, where are you going to go？
That's why I bought the magazine... I thought I should check out some places before deciding.
I'm looking after someone's child, after all. So I'll go this Sunday.
(▲高嶺＊＊▲ is so serious about this... Hm... I wonder...)
Are you going by yourself？
...Yes, that's the plan.
I can come along with you, can't I？
Why？
I just happen to be free this Sunday. Is it okay？
But, in that case, from other people's perspectives...
It will look like a date？
I'm pretty knowledgeable when it comes to leisure spots. Maybe even more so than that magazine. So how about it？
Really？
Yeah...
Then... if you would.
All right. Then I'll see you Sunday？
Yeah... Sunday.
(I was a bit aggressive there... I should go and check out some spots.)
Well, we've arrived！
Manaka
Yes, the weather is so nice.
What do you want to see first？
I want to see the rabbits！
Eh？ Even though we came all the way to the zoo？
Well... Yumi-chan, the girl that I'm planning to bring here, said she liked rabbits.
Is that so...？ Then rabbits it is！
I've never spent such a long period of time looking at rabbits before. That was the first...
But they were really cute, right？
Kind of... Well, did you have fun？
Yeah... But now I'm feeling a bit guilty.
Why？
Because I was just supposed to come today for Yumi-chan's sake. So this is not good, right？
It's fine because now you know how much fun it is. Hmm... You are really serious about everything, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
...Hmm？
...I'm sorry.
...For what？
You know, I also think to myself "Ah, I'm just so odd." It's true.
I don't do things that I'm not allowed to. But I'm still well aware of how withdrawn I am.
Unlike everyone else, I'm just not good at expressing myself...
So, I'm sorry. I know that being together with me must be tiring for you.
You're not like that at all
Yes, you're a bit withdrawn
But that's your good point
Hm, yet how come I don't think of you that way？
It's okay, because I know it's true.
So stubborn... Like I said, I don't think you are like that at all！
▲高嶺＊＊▲, you're just over-thinking things.
There is no one capable of having that much control.
And how can being diligent be a bad thing？ I just don't agree.
But...
Personally, I think you're fine as you are..
▲主人公＊▲.
I've realized just now...
If I had gone alone today, I would've felt very lonely on my way home...
You knew that, so that's why you offered to come with me, right？
I wonder if that's the case...
...You are so kind.
Always help out one another when in trouble, right？
Yeah... Thank you.
Then see you later.
Um, well... For the mixed doubles match, let's do our best, okay？
Okay.
We really have to practice hard...
Right. Oh, it's getting dark now...
Um... If you want to, maybe... Never mind, bye.
(...？ Well... I have to practice extra hard...)
We've arrived！ It's pretty hot today, so let's hurry inside.
Manaka
Hehe, you're right.
What do you want to see？
I want to see the goblin sharks！
Sharks...？ Not dolphins or something like that？
...It's strange, right？
Oh well！ Let's go to see the goblin sharks！
Goblin shark... It looks kind of like a monster, don't you think？
But, it is a very mysterious shark, isn't it？

Yeah, it's beautiful, but... all that walking has made me a bit hungry.
Hehe... I made a lunch box. Would you like some？
Hooray！ Somehow, doesn't this seem like a date？
Well, in that case, we'd better walk away from the crowds.
(That's not what I meant...)
▲高嶺＊＊▲, I've never known that you were this good at cooking. Thanks for the meal.

Well, shall we get started？
Manaka
It's my first time skating...
Really？ We should have gone somewhere else then...
It's fine. Yumi-chan had said that she wanted to go skating. So, this is perfect.
Okay, then how about you hold onto my arms？ I can teach you how to skate.
But, if I do that...
It will look like we're on a date. Right？
I'll try by myself first.
(So she doesn't want this to be a date...)
Are you okay？ That was quite a fall.
I'm fine. But it was the first time I've ever fallen down like that. Hehe！
Well, did you have fun？
Yeah... But now I'm feeling a bit guilty.

(It's finally the day for the mixed doubles...)
▲高嶺＊＊▲... Let's win this！
Manaka
Yes！
女子部員
Game set！ Count 3-2. Match won by Tezuka pair！
I'm so ashamed...
It was a close match.
Yet, I feel like it wasn't... I lost an easy chance with that double fault...
It couldn't be helped. After all, we met the Captain's pair in the second round.
What rank is our captain？
Third.
And how about you ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
...Um, first rank, I guess.
Hehe... I really had a lot of fun, for the first time in a long while.
Lately, even though I won my matches, I was just unhappy about it.
I felt that people would dislike me... But, I also felt it would be rude to my opponent to not play my best...
(So that's what happened... Then I guess it's okay like this？)
Hah！ Today I went all out and lost... Ah！
Hey... Cheer up, okay？
Let's work hard and win next time, okay？ See you later...
Yeah, see you later.
(So she's still willing to pair up with me？ ▲高嶺＊＊▲ really is nice...)
Tezuka
You're dismissed for today！
男女部員
Good work！
Manaka
Yo, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Umm... I...
Could it be that you were waiting for me？
(She seems a bit nervous...)
That reminds me... How did it go with Yumi-chan？
Oh... she was very happy.
I see. I'm glad to hear that.
Next time, she wants to invite a boy from another class on a date, and she asked me to come along.
To chaperone the date？
Yeah, I mean they are only third graders.
Third grade！？ ...Not bad, Yumi-chan.
So then... Um... I was wondering if I could count on you again.
You mean to help you check out places？
Well, there is that... I, um...
I haven't been on a date before, so I was wondering if you could teach me...
Umm... So you're asking me out on a date？
No！ That's not it！ It's just for practice on overseeing a date...
Wait a second. In other words...
Don't think about it any further than that...
I-I see...
Then when I decide on a place, I'll let you know.
Yes, I'll be waiting. See you later.
See you later！
(I'm accompanying her this Sunday to practice dating！ ...It's not a real date, though.)
Manaka
The sea breeze feels nice...
It's a good spot, right？ It's close and it's not dangerous. It's very suitable for dates.
Yeah. I think it's a wonderful spot for a first date...
I'm glad.
What should we do next？ Like, if we were on a date...
Let's see... For the moment, let's take a stroll！
Okay！ Hehe！
I'm a bit tired.
Yeah, we've walked quite a distance.
So, a date is something like this.
Hehe... Ah, sensei...
Sensei？ Me？ Was there something you want to know？ Go ahead, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Sensei, have you... been on a date before？
Me？ Well...
Actually, this is also my first date
Well, I've been around
Of course not！
That's why I'm sorry if I'm not quite reliable.
No, that's not the case.
Besides... That makes me a bit happy.
Huh...
What is it？
Nothing, I was just thinking that you're really reliable.
I-I see...
So then we're both first-timers, right？
Yeah. Ah, but this isn't a date...
The sun is going to be setting soon. How about we head towards the sea？
Yes, Teacher！ Hehe！
It's so mysterious... I've been to the sea many times, but when I'm here like this, it feels like it's the first time.
You mean like this？
Yeah... The two of us standing here, watching the sunset...
Then I guess I was of some help. Er, for the practice date.
...Hehe, yeah.
Hah, we're finally back. We sure walked a lot today...
Yeah. I've never imagined that dating would be such great exercise.
It sure was.
Thank you. I had a lot of fun.
Yeah, I'm glad.
Um... ▲主人公＊▲.
You know, maybe today... really was a date, right？
See you later.
(I just had a date with ▲高嶺＊＊▲ then...)

Manaka
...Okay.
Hey, did you know？
What？
It looks like everyone from the club will be going to Winning Burger again.
...I see.
▲高嶺＊＊▲. You should come, too. Okay？
It might be hard, but if ▲高嶺＊＊▲ calls out to them, I think it'll make everyone happy.
I don't know what to say...
I see. So, let's do some image training...
...Ready？
"Yo, Manaka's here♪ Wanna go home together？."
"Teehee▼."
...I can't do it.
No, no. It only seems weird because I'm doing it. If ▲高嶺＊＊▲ does it, it'll definitely be wicked！
...Wicked？
In a good way！ Don't worry, it'll definitely be great！
"Yo, Manaka's here♪ Wanna go home together？" ...Just kidding.
...That might be wicked.
But you told me to say it！
No, no！ It'll definitely be great！
Member
Hey, you're coming, right？ To Winning Burger.
Yeah, I am... Er, have you seen ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Takane？ No... She usually goes straight home, right？
(I see. She already went home...)
(Hm？ Who is that over there...)
Manaka
Ah, um...
I, um...
(▲高嶺＊＊▲... Do your best...)
Yo, Manaka's here♪ Wanna go home together？

Um, er... Teehee▼

You were really popular today, huh？
That's not the case....

Really？ You think so？
I do. I'm actually a bit jealous...
I'm joking. See you later, okay？
A joke... Is it... Yeah. ...See you later.
(*sigh* After today, there's going to be more competition...)

Not at all.
I'm glad. Then shall we go？
Hey, want to try Winning Burger's new item？
Sure... But, is it okay to stop by on the way home？
It's fine if we eat fast. Right？
Right. Okay, then... Hm？
Miyoshi
Ah, Takane！ Found you！
Girl Ｂ

Um... But, I...
Eh？ Don't tell me that you two are... dating？
No way！ Really！？
No！ We're not like that...
But somehow, you two look good together...
...Isn't that just your imagination？ See you later, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
Okay, bye.
Then we'll be taking Takane with us.
Sorry, Bye-bye！

("We are not like that" she said... Well, it's true, isn't it？)

Okay, you're coming！ I can't allow you to be alone with Takane-chan！
What is this！？ Hey, stop pulling me！
(I can finally go home... I can't believe I hung out with those guys until this late...)
Yo！
Manaka's here♪ Wanna go home together？
...Just kidding.
What are you doing here this late...
I really wanted to go home with you... I'm sorry.
You kept waiting for me？ ...Let's go. I'll walk you home.
(I've heard the rumors, but her house really is huge...)
Sorry for having you walk me home.
Although I'm happy that you waited for me, please don't overdo it, okay？
Okay. Be careful on your way home.
Yeah... See you later.
I like that you're kind... Good night.

(All right, I'll leave quietly...)
